[SPEAKER_00] Evo pročitaću izveštaj kratki.

607
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Neki farizej

608
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:16,339
[SPEAKER_00] pozva Isusa

609
00:23:16,339 --> 00:23:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] da bi blagavao s njim.

610
00:23:17,500 --> 00:23:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] On uđe u kuću

611
00:23:19,039 --> 00:23:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] farizejevu

612
00:23:19,779 --> 00:23:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] i priđe stolu.

613
00:23:20,799 --> 00:23:22,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je to neke žene

614
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] koja bijaše

615
00:23:23,019 --> 00:23:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] grešnica u gradu.

616
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:25,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dozna da je

617
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] Isus za stolom

618
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,660
[SPEAKER_00] u farizejevoj kući

619
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa ponese

620
00:23:29,460 --> 00:23:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] alebastrojenu

621
00:23:30,279 --> 00:23:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] posudicu

622
00:23:30,900 --> 00:23:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] pomaste i stade

623
00:23:31,779 --> 00:23:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] od ostrag

624
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] kod njegovih nogu.

625
00:23:33,819 --> 00:23:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] Sva zaplakana

626
00:23:35,079 --> 00:23:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] počne mu suzama

627
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] kvasiti noge

628
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] kosom ih glave

629
00:23:38,279 --> 00:23:39,079
[SPEAKER_00] svoje otirala

630
00:23:39,079 --> 00:23:39,799
[SPEAKER_00] cjelivala

631
00:23:39,799 --> 00:23:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] i mazala

632
00:23:40,460 --> 00:23:41,440
[SPEAKER_00] pomašću.

633
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] I sad se Isus

634
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:44,200
[SPEAKER_00] nalazi u jednom

635
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,200
[SPEAKER_00] malo i nezgodnoj

636
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:45,839
[SPEAKER_00] situaciji.

637
00:23:45,839 --> 00:23:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] On vidi osobu

638
00:23:48,579 --> 00:23:49,359
[SPEAKER_00] koja se kaje

639
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:50,259
[SPEAKER_00] koja pred njim

640
00:23:50,259 --> 00:23:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] izljeva srce

641
00:23:51,140 --> 00:23:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja je velikodišna

642
00:23:52,500 --> 00:23:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] koja je ponizna

643
00:23:53,339 --> 00:23:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] a s druge strane

644
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] vidi i Šimunov

645
00:23:55,799 --> 00:23:56,259
[SPEAKER_00] prijezir

646
00:23:56,259 --> 00:23:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] prema toj osobi.

647
00:23:57,180 --> 00:24:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] I on priča

648
00:24:01,559 --> 00:24:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] jednu prispodobu

649
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,359
[SPEAKER_00] sličnu ovoj

650
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] koju smo čuli.

651
00:24:03,980 --> 00:24:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže

652
00:24:07,220 --> 00:24:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] jedan je čovjek

653
00:24:09,059 --> 00:24:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] dugovao

654
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] vjerovniku

655
00:24:10,119 --> 00:24:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] pet stotina denara

656
00:24:11,259 --> 00:24:12,900
[SPEAKER_00] drugi mu je dugovao

657
00:24:12,900 --> 00:24:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] pet deset.

658
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] budući da nisu imale

659
00:24:15,579 --> 00:24:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] odakle vratiti

660
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] otpustio obojici

661
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji će ga

662
00:24:18,599 --> 00:24:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] od njih

663
00:24:19,380 --> 00:24:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] više ljubiti.

664
00:24:20,259 --> 00:24:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] Šimun odgovori

665
00:24:21,900 --> 00:24:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] pred nje vam

666
00:24:23,539 --> 00:24:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] ili mislim

667
00:24:24,619 --> 00:24:25,839
[SPEAKER_00] onaj kojim je više

668
00:24:25,839 --> 00:24:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] otpustio.

669
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] tako je

670
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] odgovorimo

671
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:30,339
[SPEAKER_00] Isus.

672
00:24:30,339 --> 00:24:33,480
[SPEAKER_00] Iz te prispodove

673
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] vidimo

674
00:24:33,819 --> 00:24:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] da onaj koji

675
00:24:34,819 --> 00:24:37,160
[SPEAKER_00] poznaje

676
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:39,839
[SPEAKER_00] dubinu svog grijeha

677
00:24:39,839 --> 00:24:41,299
[SPEAKER_00] i značenje Božje žrtve

678
00:24:41,299 --> 00:24:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] više ljubi Boga.

679
00:24:43,059 --> 00:24:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] Osoba koja to ne poznaje

680
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] površno ljubi.

681
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] i u tu

682
00:24:48,559 --> 00:24:50,200
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo reći

683
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] kolotečinu

684
00:24:52,539 --> 00:24:54,259
[SPEAKER_00] ili takav duhovni život

685
00:24:54,259 --> 00:24:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] možemo upast

686
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] mi koji smo

687
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] kao od uvijek bili dobri.

688
00:24:58,500 --> 00:25:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kojeg je bilo dobro sveć.

689
00:25:01,099 --> 00:25:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] slušao sam mamu i tatu

690
00:25:02,299 --> 00:25:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] išao sam u crkvu

691
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] tu i tamo nešto.

692
00:25:04,119 --> 00:25:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] To je problem.

693
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tad te osobe ne ljube.

694
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se sjećam

695
00:25:09,119 --> 00:25:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam krenuo na zajednicu

696
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:13,180
[SPEAKER_00] onda sam slušao ta svjedočanstva

697
00:25:13,180 --> 00:25:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] i bila su snažna.

698
00:25:14,099 --> 00:25:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] Slušao sam

699
00:25:15,180 --> 00:25:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] od našeg Hrvoja

700
00:25:17,019 --> 00:25:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] pa od naših dečki

701
00:25:18,779 --> 00:25:19,700
[SPEAKER_00] u malo starijih.

702
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:21,740
[SPEAKER_00] To su bila potresna svjedočanstva.

703
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:23,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam njima vidio žar

704
00:25:23,319 --> 00:25:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] gorili su i sve

705
00:25:24,079 --> 00:25:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] a ja sam bio onako

706
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,579
[SPEAKER_00] ravan cijelo vrijeme.

707
00:25:26,579 --> 00:25:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] Doslovno mi je došlo čak da poželim

708
00:25:29,099 --> 00:25:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] da im kakav je taj pad

709
00:25:31,079 --> 00:25:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] pa da se mogu dići

710
00:25:32,019 --> 00:25:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] da mogu ovo nešto doživjeti.

711
00:25:33,079 --> 00:25:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] I često ono

712
00:25:35,099 --> 00:25:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] kažem to svojim dečkima

713
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da i oni

714
00:25:37,859 --> 00:25:39,319
[SPEAKER_00] dosta toga ovaj doživljavaju.

715
00:25:39,319 --> 00:25:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] Nekako žele svojim

716
00:25:41,359 --> 00:25:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] unutarnim organima

717
00:25:43,039 --> 00:25:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] iskusiti šta je

718
00:25:44,019 --> 00:25:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači i pad i greh i sve

719
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nije potrebno.

720
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] Dovoljno je vidjeti

721
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] šta je gospodin napravio za nas.

722
00:25:51,359 --> 00:25:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jer svi smo grešili

723
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,700
[SPEAKER_00] na svih deset božih zapovjedi.

724
00:25:55,700 --> 00:25:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi ubio, ogovaro si.

725
00:25:58,859 --> 00:26:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ubio si mu privatan, civilni život.

726
00:26:01,059 --> 00:26:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] nisi ukro, ok.

727
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali koliko te puta nije bilo doma

728
00:26:06,519 --> 00:26:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] kad je djete trebalo.

729
00:26:08,059 --> 00:26:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ukro si mu svoje vrijeme.

730
00:26:09,460 --> 00:26:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si sa ženom?

731
00:26:11,119 --> 00:26:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje si jesi dala vrijeme mužu?

732
00:26:12,559 --> 00:26:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li nekomu skratio oproštenje?

733
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:17,799
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto greh krađe.

734
00:26:17,799 --> 00:26:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ko nije grešio na prvoj bože zapovjedi?

735
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] Može ja idem odluhiti crkvu,

736
00:26:22,940 --> 00:26:24,259
[SPEAKER_00] sakramente, sve poštujem.

737
00:26:24,259 --> 00:26:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] A ljubi novac više nego

738
00:26:26,180 --> 00:26:27,799
[SPEAKER_00] rođenu majku.

739
00:26:32,259 --> 00:26:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] Tek u trenutku te spoznaje naše bjede,

740
00:26:35,259 --> 00:26:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] to je s tog bezdana slabosti,

741
00:26:37,759 --> 00:26:41,259
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin može pokazat

742
00:26:41,259 --> 00:26:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] bezdan svoje ljubavi.

743
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] I tad nastaje obraćenje.

744
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on ne dolazi samo tako.

745
00:26:48,099 --> 00:26:50,359
[SPEAKER_00] I sad Isus.

746
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] Malo da šimula sad.

747
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] Uđo ti u kuću,

748
00:26:55,079 --> 00:26:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] nisi mi vode nogom polio,

749
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] a ona mi suzama noge oblila

750
00:26:58,500 --> 00:26:59,839
[SPEAKER_00] i kosom ih svojom otrala.

751
00:26:59,839 --> 00:27:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Poljupca mi nisi dao,

752
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] a ona od kako uđene

753
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] prestavi mi noge cjelivati.

754
00:27:04,359 --> 00:27:06,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ulje mi glave nisi pomazao,

755
00:27:06,579 --> 00:27:08,700
[SPEAKER_00] a ona mi pomašću noge pomazao.

756
00:27:08,700 --> 00:27:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Stoga kažem ti,

757
00:27:10,079 --> 00:27:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] oprošteni su joj gresi

758
00:27:11,759 --> 00:27:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] jer ljubljaše mnogo.

759
00:27:15,039 --> 00:27:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] Komu se malo oprašta,

760
00:27:17,359 --> 00:27:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] malo ljubi.

761
00:27:18,039 --> 00:27:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] A ženi reče,

762
00:27:19,460 --> 00:27:21,200
[SPEAKER_00] oprošteni su ti gresi.

763
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, Isus zna da su

764
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] oprošteni gresi.

765
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:27,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, oni to možda mogu znati

766
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] jer je Isus i sve zna.

767
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ali na njenom ponašanju

768
00:27:31,299 --> 00:27:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] se moglo vidi da su oprošteni gresi.

769
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer prodovi

770
00:27:34,599 --> 00:27:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] toga da primila Božju ljubav

771
00:27:39,519 --> 00:27:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] i Božje spasnje su vidljivi.

772
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:43,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je bila bludnica

773
00:27:43,339 --> 00:27:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] koju su svi prezirali

774
00:27:45,059 --> 00:27:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] i ona se našla u kući

775
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,660
[SPEAKER_00] među onima koji su zagorčali život.

776
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Farizeji.

777
00:27:50,539 --> 00:27:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su pljuvali,

778
00:27:52,740 --> 00:27:54,079
[SPEAKER_00] koji su htjeli ubiti.

779
00:27:54,079 --> 00:27:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se među njima našla.

780
00:27:55,519 --> 00:27:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nije pokazivala gorčinu.

781
00:27:57,539 --> 00:27:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] Nije pokazivala srđbu.

782
00:27:59,279 --> 00:28:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nije pokazivala nemir.

783
00:28:00,779 --> 00:28:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što je pokazivalo

784
00:28:02,019 --> 00:28:03,099
[SPEAKER_00] bila sama ljubav,

785
00:28:03,099 --> 00:28:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] velikodušnost,

786
00:28:04,759 --> 00:28:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] alebastrana posudica,

787
00:28:06,599 --> 00:28:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] pomasti,

788
00:28:07,339 --> 00:28:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] poniznost.

789
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što mi

790
00:28:12,539 --> 00:28:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo pokazati

791
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji znamo da nam je

792
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin oprostio.

793
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je da nas je spasio.

794
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] moja neka iskustva sa obraćanicima.

795
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa većinom ko Isus.

796
00:28:30,099 --> 00:28:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se zove kad bi nekog ozdravili,

797
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] oprostio mu grijehe,

798
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju što bi rekao svaki put kaže

799
00:28:37,099 --> 00:28:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] ajde u miru.

800
00:28:37,839 --> 00:28:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pusti me na miru.

801
00:28:39,519 --> 00:28:41,700
[SPEAKER_00] Tako nekako ja doživljam

802
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] mnoge obraćanike.

803
00:28:45,759 --> 00:28:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jedno posebno iskustvo

804
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo sa John Pridmorom.

805
00:28:49,039 --> 00:28:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Na njemu sam baš vidio

806
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što sam sad pričao.

807
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio čovjek

808
00:28:53,519 --> 00:28:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] koji me je mnogo oprošteno

809
00:28:54,759 --> 00:28:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] i vidilo se na njemu

810
00:28:55,519 --> 00:28:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] da mnogo ljubi.

811
00:28:56,279 --> 00:28:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam,

812
00:28:56,779 --> 00:28:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno ste svi mali prilike,

813
00:28:58,380 --> 00:28:59,640
[SPEAKER_00] susre se s njim,

814
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji ste bili tad

815
00:29:00,559 --> 00:29:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje u Zagrebu

816
00:29:01,299 --> 00:29:01,799
[SPEAKER_00] kad je on

817
00:29:01,799 --> 00:29:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] dolazio

818
00:29:02,799 --> 00:29:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] i u Međugorju.

819
00:29:04,799 --> 00:29:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sam ja vidio,

820
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] mene je ono,

821
00:29:07,119 --> 00:29:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] on me oduševio.

822
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

